item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: dan
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

...or something like this:

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.

As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Home
item.dc:creator: dshs14
item.content:encoded:
DANCE ALL NIGHT v1.5

Dance All Night v1.5 is here! We have been working on this theme for a few months since its release on GitHub. We are now ready to release what we have been working on since January.

Check out our theme features below!

Fully Responsive!

We have made sure our theme is fully responsive! This means that if you navigate to this website on any device (phone, tablet, computer) it will fit perfectly to that device's screen size.

We think that responsive design is so important these days, that is because there is a high increase in mobiles and tablets being used as opposed to laptops and computers!

Elementor Drag and Drop Builder!

We have bundled the famous Elementor drag and drop builder into our theme. This amazing plugin is completely free and is perfectly capable of building your website with ease!

Using this editor, you can drag elements, including images, text and much more. Simply hold down the element with your mouse, and drop into the page editor! Easy right?

We did debate what to use when building this theme, and we just wanted to make it easy for anyone to build a site with our theme, this is why we chose Elementor!

Updates forever!

We want to make sure that your website will always keep working with our theme. That is why we are a responsible theme development agency. We will always make sure that any plugins we bundle into our themes will always stay up to date! You can trust us to keep your site working.

Endless Possibilities!

Our theme might be aimed at DJ's and music artists, but did you know that it can be used for so much more? Our plugins that we bundle in can be used for radio shows, creative people who want to schedule meetings and events, and much more!

You can sell tickets too!

Â£45.00

Sell Tickets using the event calendar addon we have bundled into our theme! Simply link the below button to your event listing!

Buy Now

Display upcoming events!

Elementor can even grab events from the Events plugin too! From the Elementor builder, drag the events widget onto the page editor! You can then customize how you want the events to be displayed, either by colour, font family, and more!
